ActPest Control Products Act
SubjectInterim Order Respecting Ultraviolet Radiation-emitting Devices and Ozone-generating Devices
PrecisOrder approving the INTERIM ORDER RESPECTING ULTRAVIOLET RADIATION-EMITTING DEVICES AND OZONE-GENERATING DEVICES, made by the Minister of Health on June 7, 2021, in order to ensure that certain ultraviolet radiation-emitting and ozone-generating devices are registered or authorized for Canadian market under the Pest Control Products Act.
